-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Spell Duration: 13 seconds <br>Duration Type: Special<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>Spell cast on you: You feel your body consumed fire.<br>Spell cast on someone: Soandso is consumed by fire.<br>Spell fades: The fire fades.<br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>Cast time: 2 seconds<br>Usable at: 15-20 or so.<br>Reason this is still balanced (well, the numbers might need some playing with):  The effect overwrites nothing, and stacks with everything.  If someone already has the effect on, they cannot be hit with the spell again.<br><br>This weapon will perform about equal to a warrior weilding a lamentation.<br><br>The only thing needed to balance is this combined with other spells. However, I would like it to remain something that is useful against greens, and not incredibly unbalancing against normal MOb's.<br><br>Perhaps a resistance check like Magic + 25? <p><center><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/userinfo.html?char=124109"><img src="http://www.nadiar.com/pics/mistyr3.jpg"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugoladus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goladus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/29/01 8:49:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=618.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mana-free nuking - Wizard Twink item</span><hr size=1> How does one get ahold of Solist's Icy wand? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardco